 Reference Number: 229 2307 MHU Job Description: The position is responsible for the management of the mining services department. This is composed by mining face preparation, mining infrastructures management, water/tails and slimes management, and rehabilitation. They are also responsible for the development a very detailed three to 12 month look ahead plan, and for the development and delivery of a detailed capital and operating budget. The successful incumbent will report directly in to the Mine Manager. Responsibilities: Requirements: Qualification and Skill Benefits and Contractual information: